<li><a href="http://www.democracynow.org/article.pl?sid=04/12/03/1454204&amp;mode=thread&amp;tid=25" class="external text" title="http://www.democracynow.org/article.pl?sid=04/12/03/1454204&amp;mode=thread&amp;tid=25" rel="nofollow"><i>Growing Up in the Weather Underground: A Father and Son Tell Their Story</i></a>. Guests: Thai Jones and Jeff Jones. Interviewers: <a href="/wiki/Juan_Gonzalez_(journalist)" title="Juan Gonzalez (journalist)">Juan Gonzalez</a> and <a href="/wiki/Amy_Goodman" title="Amy Goodman">Amy Goodman</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Democracy_Now!" title="Democracy Now!">Democracy Now!</a></i>. Segment available in <a href="http://www.democracynow.org/article.pl?sid=04/12/03/1454204&amp;mode=thread&amp;tid=25#transcript" class="external text" title="http://www.democracynow.org/article.pl?sid=04/12/03/1454204&amp;mode=thread&amp;tid=25#transcript" rel="nofollow">transcript</a> and via <a href="http://play.rbn.com/?url=demnow/demnow/demand/2004/dec/audio/dn20041203.ra&amp;proto=rtsp&amp;start=42:02.00" class="external text" title="http://play.rbn.com/?url=demnow/demnow/demand/2004/dec/audio/dn20041203.ra&amp;proto=rtsp&amp;start=42:02.00" rel="nofollow">streaming real audio</a>, <a href="http://play.rbn.com/?url=demnow/demnow/demand/2004/dec/video/dnB20041203a.rm&amp;proto=rtsp&amp;start=42:02.00" class="external text" title="http://play.rbn.com/?url=demnow/demnow/demand/2004/dec/video/dnB20041203a.rm&amp;proto=rtsp&amp;start=42:02.00" rel="nofollow">128k streaming Real Video</a> or <a href="http://www.archive.org/download/dn2004-1203/dn2004-1203-1_64kb.mp3" class="external text" title="http://www.archive.org/download/dn2004-1203/dn2004-1203-1_64kb.mp3" rel="nofollow">MP3 download</a>. 17:01 minutes. Friday, December 3, 2004. Retrieved May 20, 2005.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.sunrisedancer.com/radicalreader/library/weatherman.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.sunrisedancer.com/radicalreader/library/weatherman.pdf" rel="nofollow">Full text of book <b>Weatherman</b></a>, ed. by Harold Jacobs, a collection of documents by and about SDS/Weatherman. This book was published in 1970 and deals only with WUO's early period. Out of print.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.prairiefire.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.prairiefire.org/" rel="nofollow">Prairie Fire Organizing Committee</a></li>
